## Data licensing note

This license covers the **source code** in this repository only. Data
consumed or generated by the pipeline is subject to the terms of its
respective providers:

- **OpenStreetMap** — data is licensed under the Open Database License
  (ODbL). Any redistributed or derived OSM extract (e.g. baked building
  geometry) must retain ODbL attribution and share-alike terms
  independently of this code license. See https://www.openstreetmap.org/copyright
- **OpenWeather** — subject to OpenWeather's API Terms of Service.
- **Environment and Climate Change Canada** (hydrometric data) — subject
  to the Government of Canada's Open Government Licence.
- **Open-Meteo** — subject to Open-Meteo's terms (CC BY 4.0 for most
  endpoints).

If you redistribute processed datasets (not just code) generated from these
sources, check the source's terms before assuming MIT applies to them.
